text: Longed Dogecoin here. 3x Leverage Swing Trade. SL 0.16, TPs starting at 0.30. If June shall be Joyful, then Retail nees to returd. This happens once Eth breaks 3k. And once that is done, Retail likely bids Dogecoin. Dogecoin has always been a great indicator for retail activity.
